Systemax - Wikipedia





















 






Systemax

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Systemax Inc.





Type

Public[1]


Traded as
NYSE: SYX


Industry
Industrial and Technology Products[2]


Founded
1949; 68 years ago (1949)


Headquarters
Port Washington, New York, U.S.



Area served

Nationwide



Key people




Larry Reinhold (CEO)
Tex Clark (CFO)





